data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-story home that offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, & an attached 2-car garage in the established community of Cinco Ranch Meadow Place in Katy, TX! Your new home offers impeccable curb appeal with a traditional brick exterior & a masterful design, mature trees, & a double-wide driveway. Upon entering you are greeted by elevated ceilings, tile flooring, and designer paint. The gourmet kitchen offers granite counters, an abundance of cabinetry, & an island with a gas cooktop and a complementing vent hood that is not only functional but also serves as an accent piece. Just off the kitchen is the breakfast nook. Decompress in the cozy living space that offers a fireplace with a neutral tile surround & custom mantle. The primary offers a welcoming retreat as well as an ensuite bath with a soaking tub, walk-in shower, and vanity with dual sinks. With 3 additional bedrooms and a game room upstairs, your family will fall in love with the design of this great  home!
